<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10678] SecurityUtil has unnecessary synchronization on collection used for only tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10678</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The function &lt;em&gt;SecurityUtil.getKerberosInfo()&lt;/em&gt;  is a function used during authentication and authorization. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has two synchronized blocks and one of them is on testProviders. This is an unnecessary lock given that the testProviders is empty in real scenario.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
